Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦  为什么要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的婚礼就要开始了 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就一直梦想着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在为我们祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪式要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走后门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后门的锁好象已经坏掉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很有趣的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫好像很有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么不满的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你不是我所认识的亚伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都拜它所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到全身的力量不断地涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们结为夫妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,え…什么啊什么啊，这到底发生什么事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人的婚礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子的婚礼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看到蕾娜根本就不愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是真心相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就一直相爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对啊 蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要用这种眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要用那么哀伤的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用这种眼神看着我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是亚伦他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有时间再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他伤得好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我…克劳德才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…这光芒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这么温暖的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不会吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么方法可以不伤害他又能打倒他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说些什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到全身的力量不断地涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你毁掉那颗石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦他会变成现在那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那块石头的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你们两个都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好用这把不常用的剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点毁掉那块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从正面果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦  住手吧  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你快点醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了  你没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗石头是在萨巴矿山发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到它的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得心底热热的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来每天都看着它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得体内好象有种获得释放的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事我就不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你是被石头控制咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像对你做了很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是那颗石头引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太自责了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股能量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事情我已经从克劳德先生那儿得知了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是那个名叫克劳德的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从他身上感到某种神秘的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓命运的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那个球体是同样的能量成分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矿山找到的那颗石头只有一颗啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…以后就不会再发生这种事咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…它能够把亚伦这样温和的人变成妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的简直就和索沙陨石没两样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索沙陨石…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从索沙陨石掉下来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就出现了很多恶心的怪物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说那是因为动物受到索沙陨石的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就变成现在的魔物了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那颗石头也许和索沙陨石有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样说会不会太夸张了点啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么亚伦的事情又要该怎么解释呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗石头绝对和索沙陨石有关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索沙陨石…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如正如小雪所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那石头跟索沙陨石有关系的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量根源是来自那种神秘能源的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能找到索沙陨石的所在地？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，请不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道索沙陨石的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查索沙陨石的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就能知道我来到这个世界的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且回到原来世界的办法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠自己的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开这一切的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 请你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 亚伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途上一路小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 克劳德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮是黑夜之父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其光芒映照出一切的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及一切虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至内心深处及黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有哲学性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说有点难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜治愈了你的伤是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被温暖的光芒所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛不可思议地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时还以为这个世界的人都有这样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只有蕾娜才拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会对任何人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候和小雪一起承诺过的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来告诉你真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜那个孩子并不是葳达的亲生女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是从 神护森林 里拣回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们夫妇一直没有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就认为她是上天赐给他们的礼物而非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜对这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我认为现在告诉她还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那孩子的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实完全都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父母亲到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拥有那种治愈的能力的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的线索就是她被拣到的时候身上所戴的那条坠子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…您为什么要告诉我这么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德 请你成为蕾娜的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜非常需要一个支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道自己身世的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她已经发现到自己与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次旅途 请你带她一起同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候有没有吓到你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你治疗伤口的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧 居然拥有那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…我也和克劳德一样…来自异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道该怎么跟你道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我认定你是传说中的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你添加了这么多的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…我也不知道该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我终于找到答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带我一起去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多艰苦我都会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不会给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很想帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 你的心意我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不能带你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 还是要一个人走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将会是很辛苦的旅程哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样…也无所谓吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我送你们到克洛斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  我们踏上了旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是魔石  索沙陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是纹章术师 塞丽奴•茱莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很唐突，克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你当我的保镖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标就是 没错 克洛斯洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  出现了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家对那种东西最没辙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德 求求你 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 星之海洋EX 纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛斯的秘宝到底是什么宝藏呢？
